{"arkId":"cl010112458","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112458","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1650","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1650,"imprecision":"","text":"1ere moiti\u00e9 du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Barberet, Jean","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7028","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; bo\u00eetier \u00e0 deux couvercles grav\u00e9s. Couvercle du mouvement repr\u00e9sentant Mars sur fond de grotesques d\u0027apr\u00e8s une estampe d\u0027Etienne Delaune ; celui du cadran figure une femme aux ailes d\u00e9ploy\u00e9es vue sur une gaine au centre de grotesques d\u0027apr\u00e8s une gravure de Th\u00e9odore de Bry. Deux m\u00e9daillons figurant Mars et Diane ornent la frise grav\u00e9e sur la carrure. Au revers du couvercle prot\u00e9geant le mouvement se trouvent une boussole et un cadran solaire dont le style est reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains, grav\u00e9 sur son pourtour de rinceaux o\u00f9 apparaissent un troph\u00e9e militaire et une femme assise entour\u00e9e d\u0027armes et de drapeaux. Centre du cadran d\u00e9cor\u00e9 du Triomphe de la mort : un squelette arm\u00e9 d\u0027une lance monte un cheval. Revers du couvercle du cadran grav\u00e9 d\u0027une guirlande. Mouvement ajust\u00e9 dans la bo\u00eete, muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge et d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq rectangulaire ajour\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris o\u00f9 surgit une t\u00eate d\u0027angelot. Cliquet orn\u00e9 de rinceaux et d\u0027un poisson.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : J Barberet\/AParis [signature ponctu\u00e9e d\u0027une fleurette]","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,4","displayDimension":"7,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"4,2","displayDimension":"4,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gavet ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Loui